WEBVTT

00:00:00.240 --> 00:00:03.934
Well, good evening, family. Thank you for joining me again today.

00:00:03.935 --> 00:00:10.946
We're going to go over some of the things the Lord showed us in this last video three days ago.

00:00:10.947 --> 00:00:17.519
I've taken some time to pray over what the Lord has been showing me.

00:00:17.520 --> 00:00:23.771
Some of the things, like I always talk to you all about, is knowing your audience.

00:00:23.773 --> 00:00:43.410
Now, what the Lord has been showing me the last 48 hours really strong is concerning the leadership in the church.

00:00:43.411 --> 00:00:49.119
Everybody's a leader in the body of Christ. You're leading somebody. There's always somebody watching.

00:00:49.120 --> 00:01:05.949
But whenever God puts his hand on you to lead as a pastor, teacher, evangelist, or prophetic voice, too much is given, much is required.

00:01:05.950 --> 00:01:24.158
As I was praying, the word has been very heavy to the point where I didn't want to come across making a video last night as fear.

00:01:24.159 --> 00:01:33.199
I want to be precise in how I'm saying things so that you can take it to God in prayer.

00:01:33.200 --> 00:01:41.947
Everything I say is my opinion of what the Holy Spirit is showing me and what I feel the Lord is leading me in prayer to.

00:01:41.948 --> 00:01:48.780
Right now, he's examining his troops. He told me, 'I'm examining my leadership.

00:01:48.781 --> 00:02:46.767
I'm examining the troops.'He started talking to me about how all the children of Israel, because there was doubt and unbelief in them, that generation didn't get to go on and experience the promise because they said, 'We're the size of grasshoppers.'They didn't go and inherit the land because they were afraid.

00:02:46.768 --> 00:03:06.958
They didn't do what God had called them to do. So, a whole generation had to pass away, other than just a handful, to go and take the promised land, Canaan—the beautiful milk and honey—but the giants were in the land, right?

00:03:06.959 --> 00:03:39.005
As I was praying, he was relaying that there's a lot of elders and people that are in ministry right now where there's going to be a real reshaping of the body of Christ. He's talking about the body of Christ as a whole.

00:03:39.006 --> 00:03:53.199
A lot of times, as charismatics, we think because we're baptized in the Holy Ghost and we walk with the giftings, he's really talking about us, but he's talking about everybody.

00:03:53.200 --> 00:04:10.639
He said, 'I'm shaking the church to awaken the church.'The church isn't just charismatics; the church is the body of Christ—everybody.

00:04:10.640 --> 00:04:30.566
He started talking to me about Rome back 1,500 or 2,000 years ago, back when Jesus was on the earth.

00:04:30.567 --> 00:04:40.929
If you were to tell them then that Rome would cease to exist in the way they were, they would have laughed at you.

00:04:40.930 --> 00:04:57.679
Nobody is more powerful than Rome. Their army, their bridges, their roads, their infrastructure is superb.

00:04:57.680 --> 00:05:12.159
But that Rome and that power doesn't exist anymore. There's a changing of the tide and a changing of things coming.

00:05:12.160 --> 00:05:24.797
There's a shaking to awaken. There's a new financial system that's about to be rebirthed, a new global digital currency.

00:05:24.798 --> 00:05:36.745
The United States of America, over the last 100 years plus, has been the top dog in the schoolyard.

00:05:36.746 --> 00:05:43.599
You look at the United States and they're the supreme military, the best of everything.

00:05:43.600 --> 00:05:55.119
But for the first time ever, I saw military things taking place on our own home soil.

00:05:55.120 --> 00:06:04.079
Not a civil war per se, but an actual invasion like a Trojan horse.

00:06:04.080 --> 00:06:16.318
I keep seeing this 'enemy within,'and I saw a wounded eagle.

00:06:16.319 --> 00:06:26.822
I saw this wounded eagle, this wounded bird; the dove that was laying had trusted in that.

00:06:26.823 --> 00:06:34.017
I saw the dove with two black crows and a beautiful cardinal that took the dove's heart.

00:06:34.017 --> 00:06:48.828
I saw a dove of peace dead on the ground, and I saw the heart that was ripped out of the dove by the two black crows.

00:06:48.829 --> 00:06:58.413
The Lord has been talking to me about the church and the shaking of this nation.

00:06:58.414 --> 00:07:23.407
As he said, 'the eyes of the Lord run to and fro.'He brought up the scripture 2 Chronicles 16:9.

00:07:23.408 --> 00:07:36.799
'For the eyes of the Lord run to and fro throughout the whole earth to show himself strong on behalf of those whose heart is loyal to him.

00:07:36.800 --> 00:07:59.459
In this you may have done foolishly; therefore, from now on you shall have wars.'As I was looking, he was examining his troops, his bride, and his leadership.

00:07:59.460 --> 00:08:35.907
He started talking to me about the shaking to awaken. From Psalm 17:8: 'Keep me as the apple of thy eye; hide me under the shadow of thy wings.'As he's examining you, he's examining the hearts.

00:08:35.908 --> 00:08:59.446
There was so much compromise and mixture in the hearts over the body of Christ, and he was calling for a pure bride to come to his side, calling forth the church to wake up out of this slumber.

00:08:59.447 --> 00:09:21.591
Psalm 17:8: 'Keep me as the apple of thy eye; hide me under the shadow of thy wings.'That's where we all should be, examining our hearts that we are the apple of his eye.

00:09:21.592 --> 00:09:39.679
2 Chronicles 16:9: 'The eye of the Lord is running to and fro looking at the hearts.'This was my heart's cry as I was praying this out and travailing in the spirit.

00:09:39.680 --> 00:10:10.079
I come to Psalm 17:8. As his eyes were gazing upon us, what does he see in you and me as leaders, like you're blowing the horn on the wall warning of the second coming of Jesus?

00:10:10.080 --> 00:10:24.276
We're all looking for the rapture. We're about to experience the greatest outpouring and move of the Spirit of the Lord we've ever seen, and many people don't believe.

00:10:24.277 --> 00:10:45.359
Can we take the land for Jesus in Cuba, Venezuela, Brazil, Thailand, South Korea, or North Korea?

00:10:45.360 --> 00:10:52.559
As I told you, there were highways in the spirit realm that we would translate.

00:10:52.560 --> 00:11:05.679
You'll be preaching in one area and then all of a sudden be translated to another area, and God will have us minister to a group of people.

00:11:05.680 --> 00:11:57.019
But taking that doubt and unbelief of the old generation because they've never seen it before—he said, 'I'm examining my troops, and there'll be some of them that will not make it to what I've called them to in this next promised land, to this revival.'I'm done with the tongue that is against—if you're not for him, you're against him.

00:11:57.020 --> 00:12:03.802
If you're not going to start saying out your mouth, we're going to have the greatest revival this world has ever seen.

00:12:03.803 --> 00:12:21.679
And I saw new young Davids; I saw new young Esthers. And he started saying, 'I heard it so loud: "If I perish, I perish.

00:12:21.680 --> 00:12:35.838
If I perish, I perish."'When Mordecai said to Esther, 'Haven't you been called to the kingdom for such a time as this?

00:12:35.839 --> 00:12:53.278
Haven't you been called to the kingdom for such a time as this?'And he said, 'I'm examining the hearts. Is there fear in it to what I've asked you to do?

00:12:53.279 --> 00:13:04.060
Who is on the Lord's side?'I know it’s about knowing my audience, and that's why I was praying over there.

00:13:04.061 --> 00:13:16.078
I said, 'Who is on the Lord's side?'because the babies don't get it, but you veterans understand what I'm talking about.

00:13:16.079 --> 00:13:35.278
And I saw a cleansing coming of older, huge ministries—mega-ministries that have TV programs, staffs of many people, and a transition.

00:13:35.279 --> 00:13:41.518
And he said, 'Some of these will not even exist in the months ahead.

00:13:41.519 --> 00:13:56.559
For some of these, their time has come; their season is over.'And you will see one that was be no more, and one that wasn't be.

00:13:56.560 --> 00:14:08.398
And I saw a rising up of new faces that will come out of nowhere. And I saw them taking the land.

00:14:08.399 --> 00:14:17.599
I saw a bulldog faith coming on people that just say, 'If I perish, I perish.'They're not worried about themselves.

00:14:17.600 --> 00:14:25.759
They're not worried about the finances. They're not worried about what people think.

00:14:25.760 --> 00:14:41.137
He said, 'I'll raise up people to fund this with creative ideas to get wealth, to fund this end-time move.'And the Lord said, 'Brandon, there's not enough preparation in the heart.

00:14:41.138 --> 00:14:49.200
There's not enough going higher.'I saw so many eagles that were plucking with the chickens, and I was one of them.

00:14:49.201 --> 00:14:57.198
He was correcting me. He said, 'You think too much about what other people think.

00:14:57.199 --> 00:15:11.838
If you want to be a mouthpiece in this next wave, you've got to fly above all this Christian turbulence and be set apart.

00:15:11.839 --> 00:15:18.398
There's no compromise in this—no worrying about what sister clipboard thinks.

00:15:18.399 --> 00:15:34.072
Who cares what sister clipboard thinks or brother busybody? Just fly like an eagle.

00:15:34.073 --> 00:15:39.199
An eagle doesn't care about what those other chickens are doing; he's looking at them as prey.

00:15:39.200 --> 00:15:45.083
I mean, that's what an eagle usually does. But it's time to come up higher.

00:15:45.084 --> 00:15:51.458
I'm not saying we're eating our own; that's probably a bad illustration.

00:15:51.459 --> 00:15:57.790
But he's looking for snakes. An eagle is looking for the serpent.

00:15:57.791 --> 00:16:05.518
An eagle's looking for the rattlesnake, the cobra, or whatever he can do to pluck its head and eat it.

00:16:05.519 --> 00:16:08.799
That's a better illustration. You like that one? That's better. I like that.

00:16:08.800 --> 00:16:15.410
The eagle's looking for his lunch, but he's not down on the bottom plucking away like a chicken.

00:16:15.411 --> 00:16:25.198
The chicken doesn't know what's coming. An eagle does because he's up high enough to see what's coming.

00:16:25.199 --> 00:16:37.119
And as we are praying over this nation, just as Rome fell, America will be humbled.

00:16:37.120 --> 00:16:48.679
America will be humbled and shaken to awaken. We have a window of opportunity. We're praying for our president in this opportunity.

00:16:48.680 --> 00:17:00.398
As he said, 'Don't be an ostrich that sticks its head in the sand.'We become so complacent with time.

00:17:00.399 --> 00:17:10.359
Yesterday's news—we can hear about something major that happened, like a Charlie Kirk thing or whatever, and something huge happens back last year—but a lot of people go back to their Monday through Friday.

00:17:10.360 --> 00:17:19.198
They've got their nose to the grindstone, and they're going with all their heart just trying to make it and barely getting by.

00:17:19.199 --> 00:17:25.678
You get distracted with the water that's getting hotter and hotter all around you.

00:17:25.679 --> 00:17:37.918
And that's what he was talking to me about. I saw something that didn't make my flesh happy.

00:17:37.919 --> 00:17:50.159
And he's looking for the people that will say, 'If I perish, I perish. I'm sold out.'It's easy to be a parrot.

00:17:50.160 --> 00:18:08.879
I was listening to a sermon—I won't say which one—and it was really good. It blessed me.

00:18:08.880 --> 00:18:23.439
Everything the individual was saying was about fire, talking about the glory, but afterward they said, 'We're going to lay hands on people at the end of the service and we're going to experience this, right?'And it was like touching a cold stove.

00:18:23.440 --> 00:18:28.036
I watched as there was no manifestation of what the individual preached.

00:18:28.037 --> 00:18:32.910
They were so excited and enthusiastic, and the sermon tried to stir everybody up.

00:18:32.911 --> 00:18:39.839
It was one of those where you go, but there was no demonstration after the sermon was over.

00:18:39.840 --> 00:18:54.719
As I watched, the Lord said, 'I want you to see something.'He said, 'This comes out of refiner's fire.

00:18:54.720 --> 00:19:08.159
This level of glory—find the scripture—for the greater glory comes by the refining.

00:19:08.160 --> 00:19:22.807
It comes by the refining, and the greater the suffering, the greater the glory and the manifestation of the glory.'And he said it's on individuals like it was William Seymour, like it was Smith Wigglesworth.

00:19:22.808 --> 00:19:40.961
I asked why it was on these men, and it was the refining fire—'If I perish, I perish.'Like Esther, like what she said, there's a key to it.

00:19:40.962 --> 00:19:47.331
We can parrot a lot of things and we can say some things that some other elders say because it sounds good.

00:19:47.332 --> 00:19:53.359
We can stir up the crowd, and people start hooting and hollering.

00:19:53.360 --> 00:20:05.763
But there's a level of the glory, a level of the manifested presence of God that I'm after. I was listening to the parrot of the sermon.

00:20:05.764 --> 00:20:11.373
You walk away and they're saying, 'Oh, we're going to have fire in here afterward and the glory of God's going to show.'And it was like touching a cold stove.

00:20:11.374 --> 00:20:27.091
You walk away and you go, 'Was that it?'That sermon lasted for over an hour and a half, and that was the glory? Does that make sense? From suffering to glory.

00:20:27.092 --> 00:20:42.319
For I consider that the sufferings of this present time are not worthy to be compared with the glory which shall be revealed in us, Romans 8.

00:20:42.320 --> 00:20:55.119
For I consider that the sufferings of this present time are not worthy to be compared with the glory which shall be revealed in us.

00:20:55.120 --> 00:21:01.954
It comes with the glory. The greater outpouring comes with pressure.

00:21:01.955 --> 00:21:12.798
He's not going to share His glory with anyone. But I saw as you go vertical, you attract to deflect.

00:21:12.799 --> 00:21:17.356
You attract to deflect as you're that mirror, and you're always shining it up to Him.

00:21:17.357 --> 00:21:25.279
It's the reflection of the mirror. As people are looking at you, you always point them to the Father.

00:21:25.280 --> 00:21:34.912
It's the level of what I saw coming, that He's raising up new voices and new faces in what's about to happen.

00:21:34.913 --> 00:21:43.199
But the church that we've always known is going to change in a major way in the days ahead.

00:21:43.200 --> 00:21:55.519
You'll pinch yourself and even look back and say, 'I remember when,'for how we've done church in the past will be no more.

00:21:55.520 --> 00:21:59.759
We're going to do something new that's never been done before.

00:21:59.760 --> 00:22:13.999
It will be fueled by fire. It will be fueled by prayer. Ignited by His Spirit.

00:22:14.000 --> 00:22:18.092
No. What did Brother Hagin say? 'Ignited with His glory.'Yeah, Ignited with His glory.

00:22:18.093 --> 00:22:31.199
Filled by fire. Tell me what it is in the comments section. But what the Lord was showing me was it's going to be fueled by prayer.

00:22:31.200 --> 00:22:41.278
And the Lord was showing me about the igniting and the last outpouring will be something that we've never seen before—where it's coming from and us being bold.

00:22:41.279 --> 00:22:49.279
Are we the size of grasshoppers in these giants'eyes? Can Cuba be saved?

00:22:49.280 --> 00:22:59.578
Can Venezuela be saved? Can we see LA be saved? Can we see Portland, Oregon have a major revival?

00:22:59.579 --> 00:23:09.359
Can we see Chicago—in the hood and the ghetto of Chicago—have a move of God?

00:23:09.360 --> 00:23:17.439
Can Chicago be touched with the fire of the Holy Ghost, with the Bloods and the Crips and the gang members?

00:23:17.440 --> 00:23:27.599
Can we see the greatest move of God in Brooklyn, in the worst parts of New York?

00:23:27.600 --> 00:23:41.999
Is it Harlem? What is it? I don't know. Skid Row. Can God come in and shake Skid Row? Oh no, we're the size of grasshoppers.

00:23:42.000 --> 00:23:55.119
That's when he said, 'I'm it.'He's killing that in people as he's examining us and he was showing me it's time for us to wake up.

00:23:55.120 --> 00:23:58.794
And that's what he's been dealing with me about. It was heavy.

00:23:58.795 --> 00:24:08.874
And as I was in deep prayer over this, he started to say, 'Brandon, I have to do something different because I'm out of time.

00:24:08.875 --> 00:24:22.255
And I'm raising up people that are on fire for me, that are just sold out, that say, "If I perish, I perish."'You're not afraid of death.

00:24:22.256 --> 00:24:28.502
You're not afraid of that. Because I was looking at it, I said, 'Lord, we see people dying.

00:24:28.503 --> 00:24:40.929
We see this happening.'I watched Private Ryan for Memorial Day and it's a very bloody movie.

00:24:40.930 --> 00:24:48.649
I'd never seen it before, but I was doing it. It was on my heart.

00:24:48.650 --> 00:24:57.868
And you say, 'Well, Brandon, you think God told you to watch Private Ryan?'It's about honoring the troops that fell on the beaches of Normandy.

00:24:57.869 --> 00:25:22.319
As I saw them take that beach and the Germans were beating them down with those bullets and they were just shredding their bodies with stuff, and I watched them men fight as they were going up that hill to get that, I thought, 'My God, what did they fight for?'They fought for us to have freedom to be able to do what we're doing right now.

00:25:22.320 --> 00:25:34.746
They fought for us to have freedom for religion, to be able to have our Bill of Rights to do the things that we need right now for revival that's about to happen.

00:25:34.747 --> 00:25:42.834
And I'm telling you, ladies and gentlemen, it takes... people are so limp-wristed. You're so metrosexual.

00:25:42.835 --> 00:25:48.441
Skinny jeans and fog machines, and you can't tell if you're homosexual, if you're really a male.

00:25:48.442 --> 00:25:58.719
Do you have what it takes to be that bulldog on a bone? Or are you just going to be limp-wristed, sir?

00:25:58.720 --> 00:26:06.914
You're going to have to have some testosterone up in here. And we're going to have to be like the mighty men of war with David.

00:26:06.915 --> 00:26:19.454
And there's so many people that have no... well, you know, I'm just like, 'Get out of my way.'I'll never be friends.

00:26:19.455 --> 00:26:29.288
Don't ever try to talk to me. Either you got it or you don't. Either you want to fight for what God has given us or we're going to lose it.

00:26:29.289 --> 00:26:38.639
Let me give you an example of why I'm as radical inside tonight than I've ever been before.

00:26:38.640 --> 00:26:46.840
I want to read this. Move over, baby. I can't see it. Fueled by prayer.

00:26:46.841 --> 00:26:54.639
Fired by the spirit. Ignited with the glory. Fueled by prayer.

00:26:54.640 --> 00:27:01.222
Fired by the spirit. Ignited with his glory. Now you want to know why I'm passionate tonight.

00:27:01.223 --> 00:27:09.796
And you say, 'Well, what do you mean by being limp-wristed?'I'm talking about people who are just passively getting by and you have no testosterone.

00:27:09.797 --> 00:27:16.136
You're a weak, wimpy man. That's what I'm talking about. This is the trash I'm talking about.

00:27:16.137 --> 00:27:25.336
I want to show you what happened in England today. And this is coming to America. This is coming to America if you don't wake up.

00:27:25.337 --> 00:27:35.759
I'm telling you, this is the trash they're going to push on our kids in the coming days.

00:27:35.760 --> 00:27:45.108
In England, they're taking them... here, play. So public school systems do this now, huh?

00:27:45.109 --> 00:28:09.106
So you want to let your kids learn how to be Islam? Limp-wristed men let that happen. Good for him. Do you see it? That's what I'm talking about.

00:28:09.107 --> 00:28:16.079
They're going to push it down your throat and you're either going to swallow it or you're going to spew it all over them.

00:28:16.080 --> 00:28:24.639
You're not going to ever cause my kids to bow down to a false god.

00:28:24.640 --> 00:28:30.798
The only person who ever died for you was Jesus Christ. And there's no other way to the Father except through him.

00:28:30.799 --> 00:28:36.239
Muhammad didn't save you. Buddha didn't save you. The devil can't help you.

00:28:36.240 --> 00:28:47.678
There's no other religion other than the Lord Jesus Christ. There's no other way to the Father other than him.

00:28:47.679 --> 00:28:57.599
Good for that young man for saying, 'I ain't bowing to your false god.'But this is what I'm trying to tell you.

00:28:57.600 --> 00:29:03.278
As the church is so passive, people get upset when I talk about having firearms.

00:29:03.279 --> 00:29:07.829
I got firearms all around me all the time. I carry a gun on me. I carry a gun in my car.

00:29:07.830 --> 00:29:19.513
I got more clips than I've got toothpaste in my house. I'm telling you, people get mad at me.

00:29:19.514 --> 00:29:25.959
Get mad. Go away. I don't care. I don't want you here. But I'm going to tell you, if you don't get radical for Jesus...

00:29:25.960 --> 00:29:29.806
you say, 'Well, what does that have to do?'Because our founding fathers...

00:29:29.807 --> 00:29:38.169
well, the ones that died on the beach of Normandy, and George Washington that suffered, and their troops all fought for your freedom.

00:29:38.170 --> 00:29:45.439
Every single one of them died on that battlefield. But they didn't do it with an ink pen.

00:29:45.440 --> 00:29:50.588
They didn't do it, sister, with a little clipboard. They did it with a musket.

00:29:50.589 --> 00:29:57.028
Some of them with not very good rifles from what I was watching.

00:29:57.029 --> 00:30:08.158
But it took some guts to take the land and say, 'No, you're not going to kill all these Jews.

00:30:08.159 --> 00:30:22.479
No, we're not all going to be speaking German.'And now there's a lot of God-fearing Germans that watch me, but Hitler was a tyrant.

00:30:22.480 --> 00:30:34.879
And the same kind of Antichrist spirit is coming again. And as long as we are here, we will occupy and take the land for Jesus.

00:30:34.880 --> 00:30:44.461
And we pray and we intercede. But there's going to have to be some of that bulldog faith that says, 'No, not in my house.

00:30:44.462 --> 00:30:54.291
You're not doing this.'As you see these little kids bowing down to Muhammad, the false gods in schools, and you go, 'What is going on?

00:30:54.292 --> 00:31:12.578
Is that normal?'No, that's not normal. It bothers me a lot. And maybe you're watching the wrong channel because I'm not going to sit idly by and watch schools here.

00:31:12.579 --> 00:31:21.199
I'm going to pray. I'm going to do what we got to do. You say, 'Well, Brandon, what do you think we should do?'We got to speak out at our school boards.

00:31:21.200 --> 00:31:30.083
I'm not talking about people getting violent, but I'm talking about whenever it comes down to our war and what's going on right now.

00:31:30.084 --> 00:31:44.798
We're fighting an enemy that has more of a backbone saying, 'Listen, we're going to fight America.'They're still crying out 'Death to America'all across Iran right now.

00:31:44.799 --> 00:31:57.385
I saw the videos and I'm like, we're trying to liberate you. We're trying to help you, and these crazy people are in the streets yelling 'Death to America'still, and I'm like, what in the world's going on with them?

00:31:57.386 --> 00:32:20.959
We're trying to take out your government to help you have a freedom to get away and they're still in the streets yelling 'Death to America.'And I'm thinking, my God, I thought, 'That's a difference in culture, huh?'Something ain't right.

00:32:20.960 --> 00:32:29.550
So, we pray for the people. We pray for our troops. As I watched Saving Private Ryan, like I saw that movie was so real to me.

00:32:29.551 --> 00:32:40.082
It shook me. I'd never seen it before. And I went, 'Oh my gosh, this is a lot. This is over the top what those men went through.

00:32:40.083 --> 00:32:54.398
Thank God for their service.'But they didn't do that and die on that beach with blood everywhere and guts and everything for you to lose your freedom.

00:32:54.399 --> 00:33:07.038
Our Bill of Rights. I told you what will be challenged. The First Amendment will be challenged greatly in 2028.

00:33:07.039 --> 00:33:18.079
Your First Amendment rights will be challenged greatly. And I saw a web that was wrapped around by a spider all the way across it.

00:33:18.080 --> 00:33:21.250
And the spider had built a web all around the First Amendment.

00:33:21.251 --> 00:33:27.788
And it was trying to come after the Second Amendment. And it had a black line and it couldn't get through it.

